### ============================================================
### Dewflow Backend — 完整 API 本地真实测试
### ============================================================
###
### 前置准备（按顺序执行）：
###   1. make env-smoke-prepare       — 生成 .env.smoke + secrets
###   2. make set-llm PROVIDER=mock   — 设为 mock（无需真实 LLM key）
###      或 make set-llm PROVIDER=gemini — 设为 Gemini（需输入 API key）
###   3. make image-build              — 构建 Docker 镜像
###   4. make env-smoke-up             — 启动完整栈
###   5. make env-smoke-wait           — 等待就绪
###   6. make seed-dev                 — 灌入种子数据
###
### 使用方式：
###   在 VS Code REST Client 中从上到下依次执行请求
###   依赖前序请求的响应变量（token、id 等）
###
### 验证要点：
###   - 每个 ### 块旁标注了期望状态码和关键字段
###   - "应该失败" 的请求明确标注期望的 4xx 状态码
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@seedPassword = SeedPass123!
@adminUsername = seed_admin
@memberUsername = seed_member
@viewerUsername = seed_viewer
@inactiveUsername = seed_inactive
@workspaceAdminUsername = seed_workspace_admin


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 0. 健康检查 — 无需认证
### 期望: 200 + {"status": "alive"}
### ----------------------------------------------------------

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health_check/live
Accept: application/json

### 健康检查 — DB 就绪
### 期望: 200 + {"status": "ready", "latency_ms": <number>}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health_check/db_ready
Accept: application/json


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 1. 认证 — 注册 & 登录
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 1.1 注册新用户
### 期望: 200 + UserResponse（含 id, username, is_active=true, is_superuser=false）
# @name registerNewUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_rest_user",
  "email": "test_rest_user@example.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "confirm_password": "TestPass123!"
}

### 1.2 重复注册同用户名 — 应该失败
### 期望: 400 或 409（用户已存在）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_rest_user",
  "email": "test_rest_user@example.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "confirm_password": "TestPass123!"
}

### 1.3 注册短用户名 — 应该失败（< 3 chars）
### 期望: 422（验证错误）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ab",
  "email": "ab@example.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "confirm_password": "TestPass123!"
}

### 1.4 Admin 登录
### 期望: 200 + {"access_token": "...", "token_type": "bearer"}
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{adminUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}

### 1.5 Member 登录
# @name memberLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{memberUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}

### 1.6 Viewer 登录
# @name viewerLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{viewerUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}

### 1.7 Workspace Admin 登录
# @name wsAdminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{workspaceAdminUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}

### 1.8 Inactive 用户登录 — 应该失败
### 期望: 400（用户未激活）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{inactiveUsername}}&password={{seedPassword}}

### 1.9 错误密码登录 — 应该失败
### 期望: 401 或 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{adminUsername}}&password=WrongPassword123!


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 2. 用户管理
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 2.1 Admin 查看当前用户
### 期望: 200 + UserResponse（is_superuser=true）
# @name adminMe
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2.2 Member 查看当前用户
### 期望: 200 + UserResponse（is_superuser=false）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2.3 Admin 按用户名查询用户
### 期望: 200 + UserResponse
# @name memberLookup
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?username={{memberUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2.4 Admin 按邮箱查询用户
### 期望: 200 + UserResponse
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?email=seed_member@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2.5 Admin 修改用户 — 修改 max_tokens
### 期望: 200 + UserResponse（max_tokens=90000）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{memberLookup.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "max_tokens": 90000
}

### 2.6 Admin 创建用户
### 期望: 200 + UserResponse
# @name adminCreateUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_created_user1",
  "email": "admin_created1@example.com",
  "password": "AdminCreated123!",
  "confirm_password": "AdminCreated123!"
}

### 2.7 Member 查询用户列表 — 应该失败
### 期望: 403（非 superuser 无权查询）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?username={{adminUsername}}
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2.8 无 token 访问 /users/me — 应该失败
### 期望: 401 或 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Accept: application/json

### 2.9 无效 token 访问 — 应该失败
### 期望: 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid.jwt.token
Accept: application/json


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 3. 工作空间
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 3.1 Admin 创建工作空间（用于后续成员管理测试）
### 期望: 201 + WorkspaceResponse
### 后续第 4 节成员管理全部引用此工作空间的 id
# @name createWorkspace
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "REST 测试工作空间",
  "slug": "rest-test-workspace"
}

### 3.2 列出工作空间
### 期望: 200 + WorkspaceListResponse
# @name listWorkspaces
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 3.3 获取单个工作空间
### 期望: 200 + WorkspaceResponse
# @name getWorkspace
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/{{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 3.4 更新工作空间
### 期望: 200 + WorkspaceResponse（name 已更新）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/{{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "REST 测试工作空间-已更新"
}

### 3.5 查看种子工作空间列表
### 期望: 200 + WorkspaceListResponse
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces?skip=0&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 4. 工作空间成员管理
### （使用 3.1 创建的工作空间，admin 是 owner）
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 4.1 查看工作空间成员
### 期望: 200 + WorkspaceMemberListResponse
# @name listMembers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/{{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}/members?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 4.2 添加 Member 到工作空间
### 期望: 201 + WorkspaceMemberResponse（role=member）
# @name addMember
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/{{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{memberLookup.response.body.$.id}}",
  "role": "member"
}

### 4.3 修改成员角色
### 期望: 200 + WorkspaceMemberResponse（role=admin）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/{{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}/members/{{memberLookup.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

### 4.4 Viewer 尝试管理成员 — 应该失败（权限不足）
### 期望: 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/{{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{memberLookup.response.body.$.id}}",
  "role": "viewer"
}

### 4.5 移除成员
### 期望: 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/{{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}/members/{{memberLookup.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 5. Chat — 对话
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 5.1 非流式对话（新建 session）
### 期望: 200 + ChatQueryResponse（含 session_id, answer）
# @name chatQuery
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "你好，这是一条 REST Client 测试消息，请回复确认。",
  "client_request_id": "rest-client-test-001"
}

### 5.2 非流式对话（续接 session）
### 期望: 200 + 同一个 session_id
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "请确认你记住了上一轮对话的内容。",
  "session_id": "{{chatQuery.response.body.$.session_id}}",
  "client_request_id": "rest-client-test-002"
}

### 5.3 幂等性测试 — 相同 client_request_id 重复发送
### 期望: 200（应返回相同的逻辑响应）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "你好，这是一条 REST Client 测试消息，请回复确认。",
  "client_request_id": "rest-client-test-001"
}

### 5.4 流式对话
### 期望: 200 + SSE text/event-stream
### 注意: REST Client 对 SSE 的支持有限，建议用 curl 验证：
###   curl -N -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>" \
###     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
###     -d '{"query":"流式测试"}' \
###     http://localhost:8000/api/v1/chat/query_stream
# @name chatStream
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_stream
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "请用流式方式回复：这是一条流式测试。",
  "session_id": "{{chatQuery.response.body.$.session_id}}"
}

### 5.5 列出对话 session
### 期望: 200 + SessionListResponse
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/sessions?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 5.6 查看 session 详情
### 期望: 200 + SessionDetailResponse（含 messages 列表）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/sessions/{{chatQuery.response.body.$.session_id}}?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 5.7 带 thinking 配置的对话
### 期望: 200 + ChatQueryResponse
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "请展示 thinking 模式。",
  "extra_body": {
    "thinking": {
      "type": "enabled"
    }
  }
}


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 6. 知识库 & 文件上传
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 6.1 上传文件到默认知识库
### 期望: 202 + KnowledgeUploadResponse（含 task_id, file_id）
# @name uploadDefault
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge/default/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=RestClientBoundary

--RestClientBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_knowledge1.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

# 测试知识文档test2

测试知识文档test2这是一个用于 REST Client 测试的知识文档。
包含 Dewflow 后端 API 的测试用例。

## 功能列表
- 用户认证
- 工作空间管理
- 对话系统
- 知识库上传
--RestClientBoundary--

### 6.2 上传文件到指定知识库
### 使用 6.1 默认知识库上传返回的 kb_id，避免依赖本地历史 ID

### 期望: 202 + KnowledgeUploadResponse
# @name uploadToKb
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge/bases/{{uploadDefault.response.body.$.kb_id}}/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=KbUploadBoundary

--KbUploadBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="kb_test_doc.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

知识库专属测试文档内容。
--KbUploadBoundary--

### 6.3 查询上传任务状态
### 期望: 200 + TaskResponse（含 status, progress）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge/tasks/{{uploadDefault.response.body.$.task_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 6.4 查询文件状态
### 期望: 200 + KnowledgeFileResponse（含 filename, status）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/knowledge/files/{{uploadDefault.response.body.$.file_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 6.5 上传超大文件 — 超过 KNOWLEDGE_MAX_UPLOAD_SIZE_MB (默认 20MB)
### REST Client 无法构造超大 body，建议用 curl 验证：
###   dd if=/dev/zero bs=1M count=21 | curl -X POST \
###     -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>" \
###     -F "file=@-;filename=huge.bin" \
###     http://localhost:8000/api/v1/knowledge/default/upload

### 6.6 验证 RAG 命中刚上传的知识库
# @name ragHitQuery
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "根据刚上传的知识文档，Dewflow 后端 API 的功能列表有哪些？只列出文档中的条目。",
  "kb_id": "{{uploadDefault.response.body.$.kb_id}}",
  "client_request_id": "rag-hit-001"
}
### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 7. 审计日志
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 7.1 Admin 查询审计事件
### 期望: 200 + AuditEventListResponse
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 7.2 按 action 过滤
### 期望: 200 + 过滤后的结果
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?action=workspace.seed&skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 7.3 按 outcome 过滤
### 期望: 200 + 只有 denied 结果
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?outcome=denied&skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 7.4 按 request_id 过滤
### 期望: 200 + 0 或 1 条结果
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?request_id=seed-audit-001
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 7.5 按 workspace_id 过滤
### 期望: 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?workspace_id={{createWorkspace.response.body.$.id}}&skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 7.6 Member 查询审计 — 应该失败（无 audit:read 权限）
### 期望: 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/audit/events?skip=0&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 8. 权限策略
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 8.1 查看权限策略
### 期望: 200 + PermissionPolicyResponse（含 permissions, roles, role_permissions）
# @name permissionPolicy
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions/policy
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 8.2 未认证访问权限策略 — 应该失败
### 期望: 401 或 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions/policy
Accept: application/json


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 9. 用户 CSV 导入（Superuser only）
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 9.1 Admin 上传 CSV 导入用户
### 期望: 200 + UserImportResponse（含 total_rows, imported_rows）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/csv_upload
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=CsvBoundary

--CsvBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="users.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

username,email,password
csv_user1,csv_user1@example.com,CsvPass123!
csv_user2,csv_user2@example.com,CsvPass123!
--CsvBoundary--

### 9.2 Member 上传 CSV — 应该失败
### 期望: 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/csv_upload
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=CsvBoundary2

--CsvBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="users.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

username,email,password
csv_user3,csv_user3@example.com,CsvPass123!
--CsvBoundary2--


### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 10. 边界 & 错误场景汇总
### ----------------------------------------------------------

### 10.1 无效 UUID 路径参数
### 期望: 422
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 10.2 不存在的资源
### 期望: 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### 10.3 空查询字符串
### 期望: 422（query 最少 1 字符）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/query_sent
Authorization: Bearer {{memberLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "   "
}

### 10.4 slug 格式不合法
### 期望: 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bad Slug Test",
  "slug": "invalid slug!"
}

### 10.5 密码不匹配
### 期望: 422
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "pwd_mismatch_user",
  "email": "pwd_mismatch@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirm_password": "DifferentPassword!"
}
